{"tid":2379674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【香港韭菜】佐敦小店東主嘆損失慘重","createTime":"2021-01-25T11:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:16:06.000Z","uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06a4990aa3345899c6e37eb7d667867174b31801","tid":2379674,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">【封區過後】小店東主嘆損失慘重 冀政府補償 「講咩過年呀，過身就有！」<br />\n<br />\n2021/1/25 &mdash; 12:51</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/202101125-15_YeNm9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F202101125-15_YeNm9_1200x0.png&h=bfc020f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n<br />\n油麻地佐敦四街「封區」48 小時，至今晨 4 時終解封，惟今早仍有大批身穿白色保護衣的工作人員在各大廈門外駐守，有區內包點店店主羅先生表示，街道上「白衣人」比市民更多，「邊個夠膽嚟食嘢啊？咪又係做唔到生意」，更稱<span class=\"red\">「仲講咩過年呀，過身就有！」</span>但亦有魚檔檔主認為，檢測能找出染病者，避免進一步傳播病毒，「叫做好過無囉」。<br />\n<br />\n在上海街經營蒸包店 8 年的羅先生憶述，兩日前凌晨 4 時，正下樓準備開店，突然被禁止離開大廈，只能回家，<span class=\"red\">「自己鬧自己抵死，點解要係油麻地開鋪？」</span>他批評政府公布安排不理想，「你封唔緊要，早啲通知嘛」，「兩日唔開，人工損失、鋪租損失、貨錢損失，都有成萬蚊」。即使該區今日已解封，惟區內仍有白色保護衣工作人員駐守，「白衣人仲多過普通人，邊個夠膽嚟食嘢啊？咪又係做唔到生意」，羅先生又質疑食環署人員為何要待今早才清潔洗地，「解封前唔洗，點解係要等人哋開舖開工先嚟洗？」<br />\n<br />\n他表示在疫情下本身生意已欠佳，<span class=\"red\">「而家直情係雪上加霜 、靜上加靜」</span>，擔心捱不到過年，「仲講咩過年呀，過身就有」、<span class=\"red\">「無希望啦，得絕望」</span>。他期望政府可以「補償多少」，「當係可憐下我哋小商戶啦。」<br />\n<br />\n全文內容：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C-%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97%E6%9D%B1%E4%B8%BB%E5%98%86%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%85%98%E9%87%8D-%E5%86%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%A3%9C%E5%84%9F-%E8%AC%9B%E5%92%A9%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%91%80-%E9%81%8E%E8%BA%AB%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89/?fbclid=IwAR2_Yn7YDXPK0KuaAjejXaPWSa8xrquteJgQ8-FqxDRdXgbKdqpZaGziurU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2598%2586%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2587%258D-%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%2584%259F-%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2592%25A9%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2591%2580-%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2_Yn7YDXPK0KuaAjejXaPWSa8xrquteJgQ8-FqxDRdXgbKdqpZaGziurU&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=5e653048\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2598%2586%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2587%258D-%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%2584%259F-%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2592%25A9%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2591%2580-%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2_Yn7YDXPK0KuaAjejXaPWSa8xrquteJgQ8-FqxDRdXgbKdqpZaGziurU&h=10420c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C-%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97%E6%9D%B1%E4%B8%BB%E5%98%86%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%85%98%E9%87%8D-%E5%86%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%A3%9C%E5%84%9F-%E8%AC%9B%E5%92%A9%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%91%80-%E9%81%8E%E8%BA%AB%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89/?fbclid=IwAR2_Yn7YDXPK0KuaAjejXaPWSa8xrquteJgQ8-FqxDRdXgbKdqpZaGziurU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">聽党話 跟党走</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53NLUUV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53NLUUV.gif&h=581bc21a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}